<div class="container mt-4">
  <h3 style="text-align: Left;"> <%= image_tag(asset_path("scilifelab/transfericon-black.png"), alt: "community", size: "45x45") %>
    Training Community</h3>

</div>


<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <div class="col-md-12 mb-2">

        <p>The Training Hub has developed and co-created courses that specifically help the
          community of experts in our ecosystem to effectively deliver their knowledge and foster an
          environment of continuous learning!
        </p>

        <!-- bootstrap accordion-->
        <div class="panel-group" id="trainer_community_accordion">
          <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
              <h4 class="panel-title">
                <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#trainer_community_accordion" href="#trainer_community_accordion_collapse1">Train the Trainer – quick-start teaching and learning best practices</a>
              </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="trainer_community_accordion_collapse1" class="panel-collapse collapse in">
              <div class="panel-body">
                Train the Trainer is a course in foundational pedagogics for life scientists and allied professionals. Check out the <a href="https://www.scilifelab.se/event/scilifelab-train-the-trainer-course/" target="_blank"> course website</a>, next offering announced soon!
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
              <h4 class="panel-title">
                <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#trainer_community_accordion" href="#trainer_community_accordion_collapse2">Organizational Learning – how learning and memory works in teams</a>
              </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="trainer_community_accordion_collapse2" class="panel-collapse collapse">
              <div class="panel-body">
                Organizational Learning is a course on developing learning at the institutional level. Check out the <a href="https://www.scilifelab.se/event/organisational-learning/" target="_blank"> course website</a>, next offering announced soon!.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
              <h4 class="panel-title">
                <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#trainer_community_accordion" href="#trainer_community_accordion_collapse3">FAIR Material by Design – create learning designed for Open science</a>
              </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="trainer_community_accordion_collapse3" class="panel-collapse collapse">
              <div class="panel-body">FAIR Training by Design are community standards that training activities at SciLifeLab should meet in order to ensure quality, sustainable training within the ecosystem. Please see the <%= link_to 'fair page', fair_path, target: '_blank' %> to learn more.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- end bootstrap accordion-->


        <div class="support-box text-left d-flex flex-column p-3">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-2">
              <%= image_tag(asset_path("scilifelab/fika-snap.png"), alt: 'TH fika', width: '80px') %>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-10">
              <h5 style="color:black;">
                <b>SciLifeLab Training Hub Drop-in Fika</b>
                <br>
                <ul>
                  <li> Join
                    us <%= link_to "Thursday afternoons at 3pm", "https://www.scilifelab.se/organizer/training-hub/", target: "_blank", rel: "noopener noreferrer" %>
                    for discussions on training and learning
                  </li>
                  <li> Watch presentations
                    from <%= link_to "previous Fika discussions on YouTube", "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4oquXWFSYSE&list=PL1nnHOyxN_WeCYjyo0Fkc11mTumm72Ozo", target: "_blank", rel: "noopener noreferrer" %>
                    !
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </h5>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="support-box text-left d-flex flex-column p-3">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-2">
              <%= image_tag(asset_path("scilifelab/ELIXIRcommunities.png"), alt: 'guide', size: '80x100') %>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-10">
              <h5 style="color:black;">
                <b>External Focus Groups and Communities</b>
                <br>
                <ul>
                  <li>
                    <%= link_to "Join focus groups", "https://elixir-europe.org/what-we-offer/work-together", target: "_blank", rel: "noopener noreferrer" %>
                    on
                    <%= link_to "Learning Paths", "https://elixir-europe.org/focus-groups/learning-paths", target: "_blank", rel: "noopener noreferrer" %>
                    or
                    <%= link_to "FAIR Training", "https://elixir-europe.org/focus-groups/fair-training", target: "_blank", rel: "noopener noreferrer" %>
                    to take part in building European training through ELIXIR
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    Join the
                    <%= link_to "Life Science Trainers Slack", "https://lifescitraining.slack.com/join/shared_invite/enQtNDc2NDk2NzMyNjkyLTA0Zjk5YzAwN2RlMTQyODg3NWJhMzhlY2NkY2I3MzBkZDhlOTY4OTIxYWFjNjQ2MjQ1N2VhYTFhYmU1ZDJiOTc#/shared-invite/email", target: "_blank", rel: "noopener noreferrer" %>
                    for an international community of short-format trainers
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </h5>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row text-center">
        <br>
        <p>For more updates, subscribe to the
          <%= link_to "Training Hub Newsletter", "https://forms.gle/d3mHw2TGaQLFxS7c7", target: "_blank", rel: "noopener noreferrer" %>
          !</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-4">
      <%= image_tag(asset_path("scilifelab/OL-catteaching.jpg"), alt: 'organizational learning', width: '350px') %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
